data.description: Seller's Loan is assumable. Seller (with a full price offer) will contribute up to $8000 towards closing cost or by-down. Escape to the serene countryside and make this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home your new haven. Nestled on a picturesque 2 leveled-acre property, this ready-to-move-in residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and rustic beauty. Plus, as an added bonus, there's a camper in the backyard that's yours to enjoy for free! Located just minutes away from Hiram, Downtown Powder Springs, and Marietta Square, as well as an abundance of shopping options, this home is all about convenience without sacrificing the peacefulness of rural living.  As you approach, a beautiful front porch beckons you to step inside and make yourself at home. The master bedroom is conveniently located on the main floor for easy access. You'll find the laundry and mudroom just steps away from the kitchen, making daily chores a breeze.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, equipped with stainless steel appliances, and a huge butcher block island is open to the spacious living area, complete with a gorgeous country-style cast iron fireplace. Whether you're preparing meals or enjoying family time, this open layout is perfect.  Step out onto the deck at the back of the house, where you can host gatherings and enjoy a stunning view of your private and pastoral backyard. If you've ever dreamed of having a horse, there's even a small barn ready for your equestrian adventures. And for those who want to try their hand at raising chickens, there's a charming little chicken coop waiting for you.  Don't miss the opportunity to experience country living at its finest while still being close to all the amenities you need. This property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and rustic charm. Schedule a visit and make this beautiful countryside retreat your forever home today!  The property was rented out, so the property tax should be much lower!!
